    "translatedContent": "## 🎼 एक-वाक्य सारांश  "
  },
  {
    "row": 58,
    "rowsha": "/PRNClULfdL1UPApN0DWLYth7f+0Q7owqCHtOcPAEog=",
    "originContent": "## 🎼 One-sentence Summary  ",
    "translatedContent": "BACH पहला **मानव-संपादित**, **बार-स्तरीय** प्रतीकात्मक गीत जनरेटर है:  "
  },
  {
    "row": 59,
    "rowsha": "n/Sc7I2kUtUq3tH86tQhi5o43XrZrFpB+gsHdoro+jk=",
    "originContent": "BACH is the first **human-editable**, **bar-level** symbolic song generator:  ",
    "translatedContent": "LLM गीत लिखता है → ट्रांसफॉर्मर ABC स्कोर उत्पन्न करता है → तैयार रेंडरर्स **मिनटों-लंबी, Suno-स्तर** संगीत देते हैं।  "
  },
  {
    "row": 60,
    "rowsha": "EiW8fILuMaULDapQ11S2baH+xsUvhjbVzTy4JuW52mw=",
    "originContent": "LLM writes lyrics → Transformer emits ABC score → off-the-shelf renderers give **minutes-long, Suno-level** music.  ",
    "translatedContent": "**1 B पैरामीटर**, **मिनट-स्तर** इंफेरेंस, **SOTA ओपन-सोर्स**।"
  },
  {
    "row": 61,
    "rowsha": "YjlKPImrzjXsrYaMrNhVyFU2vsSAHIM4cfK6OCwLm8Y=",
    "originContent": "**1 B params**, **minute-level** inference, **SOTA open-source**.",
